line. Those that participate will be rewarded for effort, High playtime players do extremely well here. This eliminates all loot arguments with rules established beforehand and all players knowing their standing.<br><br>Membership will be by voting in players through an eval system. This will not apply for the initial guild setup. However on a continual basis will be decided on in an Eval forum where posting and voting takes place.<br><br>You gain DPK for attending all raids even as an Eval member.<br><br>Simple Mob policy - if its up, it dies. All events are assigned a DPK value added to the DPK of those who participated. Logs taken are posted online and parsed.<br><br>There is no GM.<br><br>Officers may be elected and removed.<br><br>Guild policy changes are posted and voted on. A certain % response indicates the motion passes. IE a change in system or priority gets posted and voted on by members.<br><br>Qualifications<br>==============<br>We are the best players and as such maintain a standard as a collection of top end players from the best guilds across all servers.<br><br>The standard is Excellence, nothing less.<br><br>- Lvl 60<br>- High end raid experience, NToV, ST, And pretty much all Ubers.<br>- FA or FA+ weaponry EQ<br>- High end EQ<br>- All relevent keys (ST, VP etc..)<br>- Full Resist of an acceptable raid level.<br>- Right Click outdoor and INDOOR Item<br>- MT should have 1400+ ac and approach or be over 7K HP buffed<br>- healers should all be familiar with Healing Bridges, and raid healing methods having participated in them an numerous occations..<br>- All char should be familiar with their role in a raid environment.<br>- All characters should be dedicated to AA XP and advancing their char in off time.<br>- High play time is a given<br>- Determined, Drive, only Excellence<br><br>The above is pretty much a given for the quality of people to be the new top end guild. Everyone has a say in the continued guild performance, goals and policies.<br><br>Dedicated functions will be assigned. These will include:<br><br>- Daily news Updates<br>- DPK administration<br>- Forum Moderation<br>- Eval member voting and tracking<br>- Raid Pulling, healing and leadership<br><br>The Roster will be formed and held in confidence prior to the movelog. In addition we will be adding as a guild for the first few weeks till our required raid numbers, and power base is reached.<br><br>WE ARE NOT ZERG. Highly skilled players in a great environment applying skill and experience to an encounter, not a blind rush of hundreds of Zerg. If you want that, stay on your current server.<br><br>To get on the roster for the new top guild in EQ - Email:<br><br>guildlegacy@hotmail.com<br><br>The roster will be held in conficence however the class and level will be updated here or on a selected board for information purposes.<br><br>Caution - if your not top end and attempt to pass yourself off as such it will be obvious.<br><br>We have a chance to create an incredible guild for an incredible experience. This Guild will be killing everything from Dain to AoW week 1. Here's to us !!<br><br>Sign up now by E-mailing your name, char, Class, level, and some brief experience. If you can perform a special function, raid leadership, Guild officership, and have the experience please include this info.<br><br>If you dont meet the pre-requirement but feel you are of Exceptional value or wish to be a part of this feel free to drop us a line. It doesn't hurt to ask.<br><br>We already have a core group, come join us. All are created and Equal members from day 1.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#112512><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/ubilebelchrumblegut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bilebelch Rumblegut</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Druzzil Ro Member</span><br>  Posts: 61<br> <font color=#CCCCC8>(2/3/02 4:28:48 pm)</font><br>